        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 17–20. Male and female Gimnomera, lateral views. 17. G. subvittata (Malloch), male; 18. Female of possible ninth species of Nearctic Gimnomera (Gimnomera sp. A); 19. G. tibialis (Malloch), female; 20. G. vockerothi sp. nov., female." ;
